I am not the original author, this is a mirror to host some of my modifications.

The original README:

Chrowety - Twitter client for Chromium

Current features:
Follow your Twitter's lists
Translate tweets
Change Twitter API
Alerts that show you the most recents tweets
Share this video for fast sharing Youtube videos
Share this page button for fast content sharing
See your Home/Mentions/Messages/Favorites timelines
Change tweet font-size for better view
New Retweet (RT still avaiable)
Save draft for all individual Replies and Update
Favorite/Delete tweets
Notify when new tweets arrive
See user profile and zoom avatar
See videos
Youtube
Twitcam
See photos
Twitpic
Tweetphoto
Yfrog
